      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Un no Elama Behrneem /\nJesajus/ Ataltja Dehls/ un ar\nwinnu feptindefmits no Wihra\nkahrtas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Un no Sewatijus Behr-\nneem/ Sebadijus/ Mikaeta\nDehls/ un ar winnu astondef-\nnits no Wihra Kahrtas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. No Joaba Behrneem/ O-\nadtijs/ Jeteta Dehls/ un ar\nwinnu diwisfimts un astonpadef-\nnits no Wihra Kahrtas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Un no Selomita Behr-\nneem/ Josiwija Dehls/ un ar\nwinnu fimts un fechdefmits no\nWihra Kahrtas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Un no Bebaja Behrneem/\nSakarijus/ Bebaja Dehls/ un\nar winnu dividefmits un aston\nno Wihra Kahrtas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Un no Asgada Behrneem/\nJoanans tas jaunakajs Dehls/\nun ar winnu fimts un defmits\nno Wihra Kahrtas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Un no Adonikama pehde-\neein Behrneem/ kurru Wahrdi\nchee bija: Eeliwelets/ Jetels un\nSeinajus/ un ar teem fechdef-\nnits no Wihra Kahrtas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Un no Bigewajus Behr-\nneem/ Utajus un Sabuds/ un\nar teem feptindefmits no Wihra\nkahrtas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Un es japulzejju tohs pee\ntahs Uppes/ kas teks us Akewu/\nun apmettamees tur trihs Dee-\nnas. Tad nehmju es tohs Lau-\ndis wehra/ un tohs Preesterus/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Tad fuhtiju es Eelifern/\nun Arielu/ Semaju un Elnata-\nnu/ un Jaribu/ un Elnatanu/\nun Rahtanu/ un Sakariju/ un\nMesullamu tohs Wirfneekus/\nun Jojaribu/ un Elnatanu tohs\nMahzitajus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Un fuhtiju tohs ar Pa-\nwehleschanu us Jddu to Wirf-\nneeku/ us to Weetu Kaswija.\nUn es likku tohs Wahrdus cecksch\nwinnu Mutti/ ko teem bij run-\nnaht us Jddu winnu Brahti\nteem Netinim eeksch Kaswijas/\nka tee mums atwestu Sullai-\nnus/ kas muhsu Deewa Nam-\nmâ kalpotu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Un tee atwedde mums/\ntapehz ka muhsu Deewa labba\nRohka ar mums bija/ weenu\nfaprattigu Wihru no Maetns\nBehrneem/ ta Dehta Lewja ta\nIsraeta Dehla/ prohti Serebtju\nar faweem Dehleem un faweem\nBrahleem/ astonpadefmits.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Un Asabijus/ un ar to\nJesajus no Merara Behrneem/\nar faweem Brahleem un ar ta-\nweem Dehleem/ dividefmits.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Un no teem Netinim/ ko\nDahwids un tee Leeli Kungi par\nKalpotchanu teem Lewiteem bij\nveelikenschi/ diwisfimts un diwi-\ndefmits/ kas wiffi pee Wah-\ndeem tappe nofankti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Tad isfanzu es tur Sa-\nwenus pee tahs Uppes Akewas/\nka mums bij pasemotees precksch\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
